SUMMARY:Intro to Swarm — How Swarm Works Under the Hood
DESCRIPTION:How Swarm works under the hood — from chunks to neighborhoods.\n\nWhat you'll learn:\n• Architecture — P2P topology\, file chunking\, and how data lands in the network\n• Storage model — neighborhoods\, proximity ordering\, and radius dynamics\n• Economics — postage batches\, storage incentives\, and spam protection\n\nPresented by Aron Soos\nWatch live: https://youtube.com/live/lkrNZJFCmOc\nDiscord support: https://discord.gg/dUS68y87U4
